{"tid":660842,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 有咩工可以留係唔同地方一段時間架","createTime":"2018-05-11T04:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T07:25:51.000Z","uid":113800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6495d60cc3a1517748f0753551802d05ebda46f8","tid":660842,"uid":113800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港好悶 好現實主義 <br />\n想搵多啲空間同空氣好難咁 <br />\n依家做緊份高壓得嚟日日有返工無放工嘅工 <br />\n好想出去抖下氣 但又唔想hea99 都無能力唔打工咁去其他地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想去睇多啲世界 一邊做野一邊見識下唔同地方嘅文化 想係每個地方留耐啲 幾個月一兩年都好 唔想好似空姐果啲好快就要走 <br />\n又唔想好似blogger 商業味咁重<br />\n諗左好耐 都無咩結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以嚟集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641faea9cea3111d42fdeb1d129f109ce15c7d34","tid":660842,"uid":126046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"空姐<br />\n機師<br />\n外交官"},{"pid":"4416e389d3ddfbd3053b98fa40a753772520b44a","tid":660842,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"做雞"},{"pid":"7ae551c43bac0379d4b3ee05f8713abdb3c97d83","tid":660842,"uid":11072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:34:14.000Z","msg":"working holiday啦"},{"pid":"55b1c04442a2246bdc196b4151a1246c6f7b92e2","tid":660842,"uid":113461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"行船"}]}